title: 11/11: Weekend Recap - Young RBs Emerge (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
How about those young RBs! Nick Chubb, Aaron Jones, Kerryon Johnson and Rashaad Penny were huge for Fantasy owners today. We'll talk about those guys plus Winners (4:40) including Leonard Fournette and Corey Davis and Losers (13:22) including Jarvis Landry and some TEs ... News and notes from around the NFL (19:15) as we wonder if Le'Veon Bell is the biggest bust in Fantasy Football history, Worryometer (23:30) for Tom Brady, Tyler Boyd and Larry Fitzgerald among others, a quick round of Buy or Sell (32:30) and the leaderboard (37:05) at each position ... We recap each game (47:03) with our Fantasy thoughts ... Email us at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
